data.description: Welcome to the epitome of timeless charm! Nestled in the heart of a well-established community, this meticulously maintained older home exudes character and warmth. Boasting 1739 sq ft of living space, the residence unfolds across two spacious living rooms, providing ample space for family gatherings and entertaining.    With four bedrooms and two bathrooms, this home offers both comfort and functionality. The well-preserved interior features details that showcase its enduring appeal, from classic architectural elements to thoughtful design touches. Natural light floods the living spaces, creating an inviting atmosphere throughout.    Convenience meets practicality with a 2-car garage and an additional 2 covered parking spaces under the carport. Enjoy the luxury of being within walking distance to schools, fostering a sense of community and ease for families. Embrace a lifestyle that seamlessly blends nostalgia with modern comfort in this cherished abode.
